data.description: Back on the market at no fault to sellers. Quiet, serene, and spacious. When you get to the end of your cul-de-sac you have the choice to pull into your circle drive or the secondary drive off the garage. Beautifully landscaped walk way leads to the front porch. Upon entering you are greeted with tiled floors. To your right is a space that can be used as a formal dining or office area. The main living area has wonderful natural light. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, new dishwasher, double ovens, a warming tray, panty and eating area. Off the kitchen is a second living area with a charming fireplace. Between the secondary bedrooms is a jack-n-jill bathroom that includes granite countertops and plenty of storage. Down the hall the sizable primary bedroom is complete with a nice walk-in closet, walk around updated bathroom including dual vanities. The backyard is a wonderful outdoor living space. Covered for outdoor furniture, complete with koi pond for peace and relaxing. Extra parking space for trailer, rv, or extra vehicle.
